content:

  • Nightly from 9.10pm until 3.55am, buses replace trains from Gosford to Wyong.
  • Trains run to the normal timetable from Central to Gosford but run up to 30 minutes later than normal from Wyong to Newcastle Interchange.

  • The last direct train leaves Newcastle Interchange at 19:45 and arrives Central at 22:39.
